## Checklist

- [ ] Client-side validation (type, size) before upload
- [ ] Server-side validation (magic bytes, size, whitelist)
- [ ] Progress bar during upload
- [ ] Cancel/retry capability
- [ ] Unique generated filenames (UUIDs)
- [ ] Original filename stored in DB (for display only)
- [ ] Image resizing and variant generation
- [ ] Modern format conversion (WebP/AVIF)
- [ ] Appropriate storage strategy per file type (object storage for large files, DB for small inline data - see Storage Strategy Decision above)
- [ ] CDN for public files
- [ ] Signed URLs for private files
- [ ] Metadata stripped from images
- [ ] Lazy loading for images in UI
- [ ] Blur-hash or placeholder while loading
- [ ] Width/height set to prevent layout shift
- [ ] Soft delete with retention period
- [ ] Orphan file cleanup (temp files)
- [ ] Rate limit on uploads
- [ ] File records in database with upload tracking
